            <sic>n</sic>
            <corr>ṇ</corr>
          </choice>u-gauravād bhaviṣyān vijñāpayāmaḥ<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> vyāsa-gīt<choice>
            <sic>ā</sic>
            <corr>a</corr>
          </choice> cā<supplied reason="omitted">tra</supplied> śloka<unclear>ḥ</unclear><!--
